query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `snapshot_execution_logs` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `scheduleId` int NOT NULL,
  `executedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  `status` enum('success','partial_success','failed') NOT NULL,
  `templatesProcessed` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `snapshotsCreated` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `errorMessage` text,
  `executionDurationMs` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  CONSTRAINT `snapshot_execution_logs_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
)
